com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.entities

Class JDACommandsBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.kaktushose.jda.commands.entities.JDACommandsBuilder

  • public class JDACommandsBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    Used to create a JDACommands instance. Although there may only be one active JDACommands instance, a JDACommandsBuilder can be reused multiple times.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.1.1
    Author:
    Kaktushose
    See Also:
    JDACommands
